creator: Hippo game
descriptionHtml:
"Jumping Zoo" is a simple but challenging jumping game.
Players need to control the different type of animals to jump forward and cross the fantasy world of fairy tales.

Game features:
1,the player only needs to operate with one hand, press and hold the screen to slide left and right, control the ball into a dreamy situation full of obstacles and strange terrain.
2,jumping COMBO design makes the game play far more exciting than many competitive games, the game rhythm is very fast.
3,the game has rich props, so that every adventure is full of more surprises and challenges.

Gameplay:
This is a game that inspires the player's curiosity.It has an aggressive game rhythm, varied obstacles, rich and varied game scenes, the player needs to control animals to move forward, avoid more dangers and obstacles, and explore the unknown.Scenes and props to get high scores.

Touch the screen and move your finger to slide left and right to control animals.
Come and try how far you can jump!

Game features:
